overview: Ring of Honor Wrestling Presents: Champions vs. All Stars from the Wings Stadium Annex in Kalamazoo Township, MI. THe main event saw Jay Briscoe, ROH World Tag Team Champions reDRagon & ROH World TV Champion Jay Lethal w/ Truth Martini taking on Adam Cole, Tommaso Ciampa, Roderick Strong & ACH.
title: ROH: Champions vs. All Stars
